projects.name: Wally-Money Management App
projects.description: It is a powerful tool that helps users efficiently track, analyze, and control their finances. The app securely connects to bank accounts, credit cards, and other financial institutions to automatically retrieve transaction data. It provides comprehensive visualizations, such as graphs and charts, to help users understand their spending patterns and make informed financial decisions.

projects.name: Medical Store Management System
projects.description: The project provides efficient management of inventory, sales and purchases in a medical store. It includes features such as adding and updating product information, managing stock levels, generating bills, and maintaining customer records. The system facilitates seamless tracking of available medicines, their expiry dates, and suppliers.

experiences.description: Built a voting web application using Python and Django (fullstack development). Designed the application for user voting with a user-friendly interface (front-end and back-end).
